<node id="Insulina">
  <data key="d0">Insulina</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Insulina, also known as insulin, is a hormone produced by the pancreas that plays a crucial role in regulating blood sugar levels. It is a medication used to treat diabetes, a condition characterized by high blood sugar levels due to inadequate insulin production or utilization. Insulin helps cells absorb glucose from the bloodstream, thereby reducing blood sugar levels.

Insulina is administered through various routes, including subcutaneous injections and intravenous infusions. The medication is typically prescribed for individuals with type 1 diabetes, who require exogenous insulin to control their blood sugar levels. In some cases, Insulina may also be used to treat type 2 diabetes, particularly in patients who have not responded adequately to oral medications.

As a medication, Insulina can cause hypoglycemia, a condition characterized by low blood sugar levels. It is essential for individuals taking Insulina to monitor their blood glucose levels regularly and adjust their dosage accordingly to avoid hypoglycemic episodes. Additionally, patients should be aware of the signs and symptoms of hypoglycemia, such as dizziness, sweating, and tremors.

In summary, Insulina is a hormone produced by the pancreas that regulates blood sugar levels. It is a medication used to treat diabetes, which can cause hypoglycemia if not managed properly. Individuals taking Insulina should be aware of their blood glucose levels and adjust their dosage accordingly to avoid complications. |</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1caedfdc556eaf26a60a6655cc1949ad&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d14439b381ec0a71696113bd127d2de&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-59f50956370c3c8d07b4ccdf2c1be920&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9024e9ddfe355e8b160c342f465a659b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-85880c91264817aba4392d3a9a19e000&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7104ff0f5a867decbe88ca957f2af13c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e518490e7f866f11cb885b9d1dad5202&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9735005c520b96f8a681712cd6b88668&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-300b98bcb5cf291f067f9020ea7b265c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-851e0a599efe470b7e37c9883ad1afef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-831d33334b41ba1642f76488d25cd3ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-257773ac7e40978613581bca72baa6db&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e84e5532f518fcabd3a299c90090899c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e3ac418d44976633b1fd0dabb42792ba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04636bf8225531316eb483ac0cb3d130&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8b4a3fc67c9fc17c6dd8529cb70bdc88&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4436a835dfb969a51419d3f9bc744a89</data>
