  <data key="d1">condition</data>
  <data key="d2">A hipoglicemia é uma condição em que a glicemia está muito baixa.&lt;SEP&gt;Hypoglycemia is a condition where the blood glucose level is too low.&lt;SEP&gt;Hipoglicemia refers to low blood sugar levels, typically below 70 mg/dL.&lt;SEP&gt;Hipoglicemia is a condition where the blood sugar level becomes too low.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-85880c91264817aba4392d3a9a19e000&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-300b98bcb5cf291f067f9020ea7b265c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e84e5532f518fcabd3a299c90090899c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8b4a3fc67c9fc17c6dd8529cb70bdc88</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1767907601</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hiperglicemia">
  <data key="d0">Hiperglicemia</data>
  <data key="d1">condition</data>
  <data key="d2">Hyperglycemia is a condition where the blood glucose level is too high.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-85880c91264817aba4392d3a9a19e000</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1767907601</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Geladeira">
  <data key="d0">Geladeira</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">The Insulina should be stored in the refrigerator between 2°C and 8°C, but not in the freezer.&lt;SEP&gt;The refrigerator is used to store insulin and other medications.&lt;SEP&gt;The Geladeira is the refrigerator where the insulina should be stored.&lt;SEP&gt;A geladeira é o local onde a insulina deve ser guardada para manter sua eficácia.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7104ff0f5a867decbe88ca957f2af13c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9735005c520b96f8a681712cd6b88668&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-851e0a599efe470b7e37c9883ad1afef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04636bf8225531316eb483ac0cb3d130</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1767907601</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
