  <data key="d0">Sensores colocados como uma tatuagem, que mostram a glicose pela pele</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">These are new types of sensors being developed that can be attached like tattoos and show blood glucose levels through the skin.</data>
