  <data key="d0">SMCG</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">SMCG (Sensor Monitor Contínuo de Glicose) is a method of continuously monitoring blood glucose levels using sensors attached to the skin.&lt;SEP&gt;SMCG stands for Sistema de Monitoramento Contínuo de Glicose, which is a system that continuously monitors glucose levels.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1589a8affdd5757e262b758cb4998689&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e3ac418d44976633b1fd0dabb42792ba</data>
